{"page":1,"results":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":81078,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"György Pálfi","original_name":"Pálfi György","popularity":0.3765,"profile_path":"/iZUOKp6V7u6G2NRTEOf3Rw0kMwU.jpg","known_for":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/sZuuEKmEdd9Emn6QIW4WiHrRjSk.jpg","id":15742,"title":"Taxidermia","original_title":"Taxidermia","overview":"Set over three generations and beginning with a sexually frustrated orderly during WWII who relieves his tensions in the most outlandish, gross ways. The result of his liaison is a glutton who grows up to be a champion speed eater. He produces a child who becomes obsessed with taxidermy.","poster_path":"/uRqxKim0Vr1JZPLYcR1rjFtu74p.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"hu","genre_ids":[18,27,35],"popularity":1.1339,"release_date":"2006-08-23","softcore":false,"video":true,"vote_average":6.639,"vote_count":348},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/rTl1x2zvz6EqwlkEo8tZ7l1a8e0.jpg","id":126314,"title":"Final Cut: Ladies and Gentlemen","original_title":"Final Cut: Hölgyeim és uraim","overview":"A film where anything can happen - the hero and the heroine changes their faces, age, look, names, and so on. The only same thing: The love between man and woman... in an archetypical love story cut from 500 classics from all around the world.","poster_path":"/eoMO14iZVBTILw1BppQu6ZHaJdA.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"hu","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":2.1587,"release_date":"2012-02-04","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":7.6,"vote_count":85},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/fm8ca5ID0dwrKB4ZTW5EcgEjvph.jpg","id":35848,"title":"Hukkle","original_title":"Hukkle","overview":"Using almost no dialogue, the film follows a number of residents (both human and animal) of a small rural community in Hungary – an old man with hiccups, a shepherdess and her sheep, an old woman who may or may not be up to no good, some folk-singers at a wedding, etc. While most of the film is a series of vignettes, there is a sinister and often barely perceptible subplot involving murder.","poster_path":"/nngXEPKlfA9PfCrscN4Xjvwx0W.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"hu","genre_ids":[80,18,9648],"popularity":0.4475,"release_date":"2002-10-24","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":6.783,"vote_count":53}]},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1485727,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"György Pálffy","original_name":"György Pálffy","popularity":0.0414,"profile_path":null,"known_for":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/dQLrjSyy64FyU8G1YKaDFA9mJEl.jpg","id":40987,"title":"The Witness","original_title":"A tanú","overview":"Hungary, 1950s. József Pelikán, who works as a dam keeper on the Danube, meets by chance Zoltán Dániel, an old friend whom he saved from death years before and who is now a powerful politician.","poster_path":"/w1jQxQykZM8wL0OTQ4fYmT9vPyX.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"hu","genre_ids":[35],"popularity":0.3313,"release_date":"1979-06-06","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":8.119,"vote_count":63},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"id":188329,"title":"There's Only One Girl in the World","original_title":"Csak egy kislány van a világon","overview":"György Bánáth landowner and Miklós Vass the teacher, on the verge of collapse, trudging all the way from Siberia where they have spent more than ten years as POWs, trying to prevent each other from falling from fatigue on the way home. Both become regular visitors to the Pálffy family and they both make amorous advances to Katinka, the beautiful daughter of the local vicar.","poster_path":null,"media_type":"movie","original_language":"hu","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.1467,"release_date":"1930-05-12","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":5.4,"vote_count":5}]}],"total_pages":1,"total_results":2}